230
00:20:47,871 --> 00:20:50,540
C isÂ Chae Yu-ri. H isÂ Han Se-gye."

231
00:20:51,166 --> 00:20:52,960
I did a wonderful job!

232
00:20:56,964 --> 00:20:58,590
I did it so well.

233
00:20:59,091 --> 00:21:00,926
She is delusional.

234
00:21:04,263 --> 00:21:05,681
Serves her right!

235
00:21:07,641 --> 00:21:12,229
Gosh, I wish I could've seen her face!

236
00:21:13,855 --> 00:21:15,774
That was my best acting ever.

237
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,609
I showed everything I got.

238
00:21:17,693 --> 00:21:20,821
-Grand Award goes to you!
-The honor goes to my agent.

239
00:21:24,658 --> 00:21:26,410
I'm glad I'm on your side.

240
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:29,246
Let's be friends forever.

241
00:21:29,371 --> 00:21:30,539
Let's not become enemies.

242
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:34,668
Right? I'm glad she is on my side.

243
00:21:40,340 --> 00:21:41,842
You are here!

244
00:21:49,057 --> 00:21:51,351
Hey Gging-ggang, be quiet.

245
00:21:53,854 --> 00:21:57,107
That's strange.
She's usually very friendly.

246
00:21:57,357 --> 00:21:58,358
I know.

247
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:02,195
She does this sometimes.

248
00:22:02,904 --> 00:22:05,490
It's OK. Don't feel bad.

249
00:22:05,949 --> 00:22:07,451
You're OK.

250
00:22:08,285 --> 00:22:09,494
Calm down.

251
00:22:13,415 --> 00:22:15,959
-Who's this? I'm not expecting anyone.
-Who's there?

252
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,546
It's OK.

253
00:22:21,840 --> 00:22:23,008
It's fine.

254
00:22:28,889 --> 00:22:29,723
You?

255
00:22:29,806 --> 00:22:32,809
Now that you have a girlfriend
and friends, don't you need me anymore?

256
00:22:33,226 --> 00:22:34,102
How did you come here?

257
00:22:34,686 --> 00:22:36,188
Why do you ask? Isn't it obvious?

258
00:22:36,271 --> 00:22:37,939
-I followed you.
-Gosh.

259
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:41,526
Everyone looks familiar!

260
00:22:42,194 --> 00:22:44,363
-May I sit?
-You already did.

261
00:22:44,446 --> 00:22:45,822
This looks good.

262
00:22:46,907 --> 00:22:48,575
I didn't eat dinner yet.

263
00:22:48,658 --> 00:22:50,452
Wait, pay first.

264
00:22:50,535 --> 00:22:52,079
Everyone paid 10,000 won equally.

265
00:22:52,954 --> 00:22:53,872
Take it from him.

266
00:22:55,540 --> 00:22:56,792
Jeong Ju-hwan!

267
00:23:00,504 --> 00:23:03,340
You already revealed your disease, right?

268
00:23:09,596 --> 00:23:11,390
He did! He absolutely did.

269
00:23:11,765 --> 00:23:14,601
I'm the only one
